{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cfca01d8c9","title":"为王观澜题词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1e79aba7fb","index":0,"year":1941,"month":12,"day":16,"articleId":"cfca01d8c9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji16","name":"毛泽东全集第16卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji16.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji16":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e427609e22","type":"paragraph","text":"为王观澜题词","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cfca01d8c9"},{"id":"c0ff1749de","type":"paragraph","text":"1941年12月16日）既来之，则安之，自己完全不着急，让体内慢慢生长抵抗力和它作斗争，直至最后战而胜之，这是对付慢性病的方法。就是急性病，也只好让医生处治，自己也无所用其着急，因为急是急不好的。对于病，要有坚强的斗争意志，但不要着急。这是我对于病的卷度。书之以供王观澜同志参考。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cfca01d8c9"},{"id":"4e15880719","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cfca01d8c9"},{"id":"d4dc6cdc02","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十六日王观（1906-1982），渐江临海人，原名金水，字克洪。1925芝入中国共产党，曾任《红色中华》总编辑、中央工农民主政府土地部副后任中共中央农委主任，陕甘宁边区党委副书记兼组织部部长，陕甘驱统线委员会主任等职。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cfca01d8c9"},{"id":"b0f8635f97","type":"paragraph","text":"乡系小孔形为水作日三六3月减前内代千刘专自三至含专三年月。时代病川之些身码用艾六等代情、如展流","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cfca01d8c9"},{"id":"c44f09dd6c","type":"paragraph","text":"对对代付病方店口为水作日三六3月减前内代千刘专自三","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cfca01d8c9"},{"id":"246cb9dc49","type":"paragraph","text":"不.专Y/M=3作对有物列足有习部六但?必隆N长月公列足有习部六但生小区","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cfca01d8c9"},{"id":"dc87f8fb1e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东为王观洞的题词","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cfca01d8c9"}],"page":{"id":"e4e646eeb8","publicationId":"m